Other Essential <head> Elements
In addition to <link>, the <head> section includes:
<meta>: Sets character set (<meta charset="UTF-8">), viewport for responsiveness, and descriptions.
<title>: Defines the title of the document (required).
<style>: Embeds CSS directly within the document.
<script>: Loads JavaScript files. 
